{"tid":566144,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"心會痛，起碼證明自己仍然活著 (Joma & 花膠蟹)","createTime":"2018-02-19T16:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T02:50:02.000Z","uid":9348,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b01e03ebb20f6ff44744c0dd92b5c57d60d1ab30","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"本貼原由 會員 Joma 於 10/26/2013 發表 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum12.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4779460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum12.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D4779460&d=Ux%2BLYFAShSwRtbfuYHZFA57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=eeaac83d\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum12.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=4779460</a><br />\n<br />\n本貼原由 會員 花膠蟹 於 26/5/2014 發表 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5145695&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5145695%26page%3D1&d=Ux%2BLYFAShSwRtbfuYHZFA57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=be0e1305\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5145695&amp;page=1</a><br />\n<br />\n現由罐頭麵包作整合 <br />\n(但有d死圖已經死了搵唔返sosad)<br />\n(唔知佢地最近點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"f30044e0dfbd1ae184cd776de44230cb18f483a0","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:10:26.000Z","msg":"係 人總需要勇敢生存  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即使眼前既花 唔會再為你綻放 <br />\n<br />\n我始終都相信 春天過後不是秋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46cf54d5259340bf60052395c761e2e930f4def","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:10:47.000Z","msg":"如何忘記你 <br />\n<br />\n　　在報上讀到，一位網名『下輩子做你一顆牙』19歲的少女圈圈，因為失戀，與四位網友相約，揹上超過50磅重的背囊，以成都火車站作起點，徒步到西藏拉薩，希望用此方式忘記失戀的苦痛。旅程需時兩個月，她每早九時出發，日行15公里，腳上起了水泡，吃的不好，累極卻失眠。『下輩子我要做你的一顆牙，至少，我難受，你也會疼。』圈圈，你猜想他會為你心疼嗎？ <br />\n　　『到底要多累才可忘記你，到底要多久才可不這麼難過。』記得當時年紀小，在失戀的每一天，也問自己相同問題。可惜，我不夠勇敢，沒嘗試2200公里的苦行，只試過在許多個深夜，由中環步行往跑馬地。腳掌太痛，便脫下高跟鞋一會，挽著手袋與鞋子繼續前行，直到終點。夜深的空氣本該較日間清新，我卻連呼吸都覺得痛，痛得開始流淚。 <br />\n　　日子過了三個月，淒苦依然，5.8公里的累，從沒讓與他有關的一切記憶褪色。反而，腳上的細碎傷痕，更教我記住怎樣瘋狂愛上這個人。然後，有一天，想起他的時候，終於不再難過得以被鏹水流過心房。曾經深愛過，如何忘記？尋常日子，偶爾記起往昔，心頭也難免微微一酸。但其實，無法全然抹掉，也不甚礙事，我們始終會活潑強壯生活下去。畢竟，沒多少人會放棄餘生所有挽著別人臂彎約會的時光，the show must go on。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9431a2ec91a168dc3c1acacf046a44d8f44b9934","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:11:18.000Z","msg":"我常常想：我為什麼要活在世界上。這樣子想常常容易叫人自殺。於是我又想，我沒甚麼理由值得要去自殺。活著和自殺同樣是兩件沒甚麼意思的事。而且，我逐漸不再去想它們。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e9de742dd93d1d37fbab9681423dba1d2403d5","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:11:37.000Z","msg":"其實呢　放膽去愛　好犀利 <br />\n你知唔知點解呢個世界咁悶 <br />\n因為十居其九都係肯學就識嘅事 <br />\n放膽去愛唔同 <br />\n放膽去愛係學唔嚟㗎 <br />\n唔係人人得㗎 <br />\n而你竟然識呀 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e594cb42a106f040bcd895a3a5c354739837deb6","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"緣份係 當你偶然搭車時遇到對面有一個人同你睇緊同一本書 <br />\n緣份係 架車下一分鐘就開 而你地以後都唔會再遇到 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bbf9f8789d448a6aea10ecb1260236fca21f6c2","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:13:56.000Z","msg":"緣起緣滅 緣聚緣散 <br />\n<br />\n怨憎會 愛別離 求不得 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cabf2ebea906d794884f9785dfa22dd9e0ce21c","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"更耐人尋味的是越到後來，黛玉的病勢越來越沉重，而黛玉的眼淚反而少了，書中寫道：一次寶玉見黛玉又在哭，寶玉忙勸道：&ldquo;你又自尋煩惱了。你瞧，今年比往年越發瘦了，你還不保養，每天必哭一回子，才算完了這一天的事。&rdquo;黛玉拭淚道：&ldquo;近日我只覺心酸，眼淚卻像比往年少了些似的。心裡只管酸痛，眼淚卻不多。&rdquo; <br />\n黛玉死的那一天，正好是寶玉、寶釵結婚大典的那一天，賈府上下全部在那裡，瀟湘館內無比淒清，只有寡嫂李紈守在身邊，黛玉悲憤交加，但此時卻一話、一滴淚也沒有了。為什麼？正如書中所說&ldquo;欠命的，命已還；欠淚的，淚已盡。冤冤相報實非輕，分離聚合皆前定。&rdquo;好一個&ldquo;淚已盡&rdquo;，此筆淚債已還清，當然再也沒有了眼淚。絳珠仙子還完淚債，已經沒有活在世上的必要了，該回到她原來所在的位置上去了。 <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實你我這美夢 氣數早已盡"},{"pid":"e036359a8605b8156f18d69023a8d9eab223b376","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"唔開心只是短暫 <br />\n日子仍可以安好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6916bcb1a7c53983c6021a1c61b7d371288285ab","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"believe what you believe, love what you love <br />\n信你所信 愛你所愛 <br />\n<br />\n石可破也 而不可奪堅 <br />\n丹可磨也 而不可奪赤 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27fb254fc0d785b1948614e8d9f0a63930f3340d","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:15:14.000Z","msg":"今天晚上，我相信大家心裡都很難過；如果你心裡真的很難過，就讓它發洩出來。你可以哭泣，但不要洩氣。你可以悲傷，但是不要放棄。因為明天起來，我們要像過去四年一樣的勇敢，心裡充滿著希望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f8afd04d2981c5602c32339385edf2a9c5bbcb","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"傷春悲秋要有限度 <br />\n抖夠就好起身 讓座俾下一個啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a694e2340fbf1fcaca3a46f01bf668a9a4a685","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"記憶這東西真有些不可思議。實際身臨其境的時候，幾乎未曾意識到那片風景，未曾覺得它有什麼撩人情懷之處，更沒想到十八年後仍歷歷在目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8aae7b2896d87549d2e009649ad41ecc4c48721","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:16:45.000Z","msg":"法國《文學雜誌》曾訪問用法文寫出巨著《惡童日記》三部曲的女作家Agota Kristof，記者問：「如果所有事情都沒所謂，那我們早上為甚麼還要起床？」自稱是虛無主義者的女作家答：「因為整天躺在床上好像不太好看，因為我們會想喝一杯咖啡。就是這樣。」我想，存在的理由，起床的理由，為了一杯咖啡，對法語人來說，多麼重要。問題不是有沒有pourquoi，而是pourquoi pas？（為甚麼不？） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  開心的理由： <br />\n何故發愁?"},{"pid":"bb3bd62cc08f200b2e4d64f4f835be927026b7ea","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:17:43.000Z","msg":"當我想起你的時候，不會打電話給你，永遠。某些錯誤，犯過一次，就不想再犯。怕聽到一把冷淡的聲音，怕無聊的對答不着邊際的問好，怕會將掛念說出口，我不要連尊嚴都失去。手提電話內的快速鍵更改了，號碼早已刪除，但那組數字依然刻在腦內，所以，習慣蹺着雙手，避免按捺不住拿起電話按下你的號碼。在快要想哭時，我會用手指劃過空氣，寫下你的名字，這是最安靜的去想念你的方法。 <br />\n當我想起你的時候，決不會找我們之間的共同朋友，問及你的近況。有想過瀏覽你的網誌你的 facebook上的資料，但可以預料，看到那些文字和相片，將會難過很久。同時，也不願讓你有機會得知，曾經有一刻，我想起你。請容許我站得遠遠，隔着一段距離去想你，掛着微笑也好心酸也好，總之，全宇宙裏，這秘密最好只得我一個人知道。 <br />\n當我想起你的時候，或許，會在 Google搜尋你的名字，一筆一畫的鍵入，然後，得出「約有1008項結果（需時0.06秒）」。你不是天上星星，怎可能那過千項結果都是你？我只想透過電腦螢光幕，凝視奪目的紅色字，跟你一樣的名字，去懷念那些零碎的美好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd288f0b3326661ec9447ff85f606e6ee4bf7710","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:18:01.000Z","msg":"當你想起我的時候，會做些甚麼呢？可會與我們之間的共同朋友飯聚，在用餐叉捲起意粉時，漫不經心問起我的近況？大概不會吧。你怕友人將此事告知我，怕丟面 更怕惹人煩厭。其實，你早將我從 facebook上 unfriend了，但猜想你會按捺不住，一次又一次瀏覽僅有的資料，哪怕個人相片的位置已變成問號。滿足了好奇，卻不開心。 <br />\n　　當你想起我的時候， 是否仍然心酸？心頭隱隱揪動，仿似呼吸不了，未至於要哭出來，但那種酸楚，足夠令你無法站起來，走出房間，看看外面的風光明媚。酸楚的感覺流遍全身，你乏 力掙扎，癱瘓在椅上，目光離不開電腦螢光幕。頁面上，我的名字成了奪目的紅色字，那 1008項結果如同巴掌，重複掌摑你的憂鬱，提醒你，這樣做有多不爭氣。 <br />\n　　當你想起我的時候，可有幻想我同樣想起你？希望你會明白，我一直沒有忘 記，只是，都過去了。現實生活不是科幻電影，我們無法超越光速，所以，回不去了。唯有拾起已刮花了的心，拍拍灰塵塞回去，然後，若無其事開步往前走，將從 前散落在身後。以後，若我企圖憑藉零碎的美好，回去起點，回到當時，寧願你已轉身離開，臉上帶着微笑，想起的是別人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d8b0dcf5030e19e8babaef8174e99d515623fb","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"This is my life <br />\nThis is my dream <br />\nThis is the reason my heart beats <br />\nI'd rather fight <br />\nEach day of my life <br />\nThan give up belief <br />\n'Cause this is my heart <br />\nThis is my soul <br />\nThis is the only love I've known <br />\nMy will to try <br />\nGrows weaker with time <br />\nBut I won't give in <br />\n'Cause this is my dream <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人生 夢想 活著的理由 心 靈魂 愛 <br />\n都是「妳」的代名詞 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86a0541dad28f65e185ddc2684e03bd709da406","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"不管怎樣，總是要... <br />\n<br />\n人們不講道理，思想謬誤、自我中心， <br />\n不管怎樣，總是愛他們； <br />\n如果你做善事，人們說你自私自利，別有用心， <br />\n不管怎樣，總是要做善事； <br />\n如果你成功以後，身邊盡是假的朋友和真的敵人，<br />\n不管怎樣，總是要成功； <br />\n你所做的善事明天就被遺忘， <br />\n不管怎樣，總是要做善事； <br />\n誠實與坦率使你易受攻擊， <br />\n不管怎樣，總是要誠實與坦率； <br />\n你耗費數年所建設的可能毀於一旦， <br />\n不管怎樣，總是要建設； <br />\n人們確實需要幫助，然而如果你幫助他們，卻可能遭到攻擊， <br />\n不管怎樣，總是要幫助； <br />\n將你所擁有最好的東西獻給世界，你可能會被踢掉牙齒， <br />\n不管怎樣，總是要將你所擁有最好的東西獻給世界。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛即奉獻"},{"pid":"49edb7b01fb90dfb556fb7e8e6712414a1fd51f6","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激你 最開心的人 <br />\n陪伴著我每個無眠夜深 <br />\n用你笑聲 修補我不幸"},{"pid":"9ecd5a9b252ba7b52efda987746eca71982503db","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:19:23.000Z","msg":"Tu me manques, tous les jours, tous les soirs　<br />\n我把你的名字　 <br />\n栽種在一株李樹下　 <br />\n讓枝葉伸展　 <br />\n向天空表白　 <br />\n我無從訴說的愛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be68d67b8b6b6ccaf80cce908db51b08008da167","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何不把悲哀感覺假設是來自你虛構 <br />\n既然失去的未可挽回 愛不到愛人 先愛愛自己"},{"pid":"e2a46f58f1501ab8c6ffffc64880d35c86d2e725","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:19:57.000Z","msg":"So how far are you willing to go for dance? <br />\n<br />\n我每日一起身第一件事就係諗住跳舞 <br />\n迫緊巴士 迫緊地鐵既時候想跳舞 <br />\n人地唱K我就跳K <br />\n咁但係我依加點樣跳舞啫 <br />\n我得返一隻腳咋 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3e8c2eafe3c0799ddfc259b7b0ea8bfc91746a","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:20:16.000Z","msg":"生命時常丟給一些我意想不到的功課，D就用「無啦啦」來形容我的前半生，說我所擁有的得到的，都是無端端，沒甚麼計劃與緣由的。 <br />\n<br />\nFollow your heart. 我常跟自己默唸的咒語。隨心而行，今天嚴厲的L也這樣提醒我。是的，有時忘記了聆聽自己內心的聲音，不小心錯失了自己的步調。有時心神恍惚依著自己也覺得奇怪的路標走，走到半路覺得不對勁，於是慌張起來。過一會，才明白也是必經之路。不要太介懷，不用責備自己。<br />\n<br />\n停下來靜下來，是想聽見自己的聲音，再開步走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 創傷會慢慢癒合 即使有疤痕 <br />\n疤痕只係你痊癒既明證"},{"pid":"174e9110e29adecdbc5c87735f8f1466cf9661fe","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢度冇camera影住你 <br />\n傷心不妨盡情悲傷 <br />\n有人願關心就儘管接受 <br />\n只要記得 不要強顏歡笑"},{"pid":"4822689296114a054064fcba0bfed9ba4ee48432","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:20:55.000Z","msg":"Planescape: Torment（異域鎮魂曲）中曾是大美女的Ravel（解密者）被The Nameless One（無名氏）的前身欺騙了感情，她變成巫婆向遇到的每一個人問同一個問題：「What can change the nature of a man? 什麼可以改變一個人的本質？」Ravel永遠得不到滿意答案，她甚至在開口回答之前就把人殺掉，因為她要的根本就不是答案，而是那個人本身。 <br />\n<br />\n你要的是答案嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a301ff3f171f8bf9e55ddf7d996ac2249b0f4b34","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你努力去揣摩一個人既心思 費盡心神只為留住佢 <br />\n難免錯過藍天白雲好風光 <br />\n<br />\n其實世界好大 好美好"},{"pid":"d93a48616e7f033fe85df39d8d11e13df4383784","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/002346_7c53e1aa81ce438bf0e8a9aff7db54ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F002346_7c53e1aa81ce438bf0e8a9aff7db54ea.png&h=ad0b28ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2047e09d0aca0d107c472a2b223eb9ebc7dfd029","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/002413_2bdcd09f2cc7f13a95ef2f4f0d47cbaa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F002413_2bdcd09f2cc7f13a95ef2f4f0d47cbaa.png&h=eeae37eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be346b9988c095de337a646355b9351716b6826","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/002527_2d7f247e8db7eb24ca59c24bb65374bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F002527_2d7f247e8db7eb24ca59c24bb65374bd.png&h=8a210f70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d66693d2a08d4c7bdc9475135a76c941878eca0","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/002718_9a7301abfb52dc5feb977716245d1dba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F002718_9a7301abfb52dc5feb977716245d1dba.png&h=f7468a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81171d0b7f8b347fb9c673fc9da2f04f6fa029d5","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/003749_9e8aeaf195ab1ecc6987863f5b7bdccd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F003749_9e8aeaf195ab1ecc6987863f5b7bdccd.png&h=4cab12bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b6cdd6f1fb0c1ef1f9e92f096a0260112d2f38","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"從明天起　做一個幸福的人 <br />\n餵馬　劈柴　周遊世界 <br />\n從明天起　關心糧食和蔬菜 <br />\n我有一所房子　面朝大海　春暖花開 <br />\n<br />\n從明天起　和每一個親人通信 <br />\n告訴他們我的幸福 <br />\n那幸福的閃電告訴我的 <br />\n我將告訴每一個人 <br />\n<br />\n給每一條河每一座山取一個溫暖的名字 <br />\n陌生人　我也為你祝福願你有一個燦爛的前程 <br />\n願你有情人終成眷屬 <br />\n願你在塵世獲得幸福 <br />\n而我只願面朝大海　春暖花開 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e602e9e7f33592c94bfe1ef93e4299402e57a259","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你不顧一切向住已經離去既愛情狂追 <br />\n何不問問自己 你既一顆心 究竟屬於佢 定係自己"},{"pid":"4d90a755cf2286d4dbaeaf70c51e4a76f3e73f8a","tid":566144,"uid":165482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"多謝你碗雞湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGood morning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebfa2a252154bce7ce0a3c467d06943b804dd1f","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d90a755cf2286d4dbaeaf70c51e4a76f3e73f8a","tid":566144,"uid":165482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"多謝你碗雞湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGood morning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"good morning<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4234ec41cf8617d6d029b21c35fba762b4ce04","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:20:51.000Z","msg":"「你不知道我多想，想你我是青梅竹馬，從小，我看著你長大，陪著你長大，一起識字，一起打鬧，一起&hellip;&hellip;到老。除我之外沒有男人碰過你，除你之外也沒有女人碰過我，就這樣，就這樣&hellip;&hellip;」 <br />\n你眼裡的光，在昏暗的夜裡搖曳，忽明忽暗。 <br />\n一點光亮，從你眼裡滴下來。 <br />\n更多光亮，從你指間滴下來。 <br />\n星星，是星星。 <br />\n一滴，兩滴&hellip;&hellip;星星從你的指縫間溜走，那麼微弱的一點光，在掙脫出桎梏之後卻好像頓時鮮明起來。好像發光的氣泡，恍恍惚惚得飄起來，卻沒有如動畫片中那樣照亮你的臉。 <br />\n它們只是飄著，飄著，看上去晶晶亮，卻什麼都照不亮。 <br />\n直飄到天上，和天上的星星混在一起，宛如浸潤在透明的波濤中，一漾，一漾，同樣的晶晶亮，同樣的什麼都照不亮。 <br />\n黑的夜，沒有一絲改變。 <br />\n而你的手，你漂亮的手指，卻止不住的顫抖。 <br />\n<br />\n在那之後過了七個夏天，我思念著女兒的時候你也思念著兒子。 <br />\n我思念著我深愛的男人，那個人已經不是你。 <br />\n你思念著你深愛的女人，那個人已經不是我。 <br />\n只不過是，我每對著星空便會回想那一夜的螢火，那一夜的星光，那一夜放走了星星的你的手。 <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到將來我們或許會明白 遺憾是一種美 <br />\n承載住滿滿的愛的美"},{"pid":"fd7fbfbfe756c9046bbe6fa85469beb18a011c39","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"沒有公平 只有運氣 <br />\n有人找到他的莫敏兒 <br />\n有人窮一生之力也找不上 <br />\n世界總是如此 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f2a618171232acd27f3412a8bee4b14ba69fc9","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:24:08.000Z","msg":"緣份是神 <br />\n遊戲，是我們 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f3e215c6c7092c7439dc3fdf27eded73b83cd5","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"離開的人 早就唔屬於你了 <br />\n你並無責任去繼續關心佢 <br />\nirresponsibility made easy <br />\n將人放低 拾回自己的愛吧 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a964fc5c8d63319b4cdada7dd949991d265ddd","tid":566144,"uid":97526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd7fbfbfe756c9046bbe6fa85469beb18a011c39","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"沒有公平 只有運氣 <br />\n有人找到他的莫敏兒 <br />\n有人窮一生之力也找不上 <br />\n世界總是如此 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求而不得 算不上找到 對不對?"},{"pid":"426d7381f9c3c880975059bbdd88de5cc79e08ea","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"You love your plant, don't you? <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIt's my best friend...always happy. No questions. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f45105aed2fc947b50dab3f4f53d78b25c76d2f","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:20:41.000Z","msg":"無法離開你 <br />\n無法愛慕你 <br />\n<br />\n我決定離開 <br />\n到最遠的地方 <br />\n在你的遠方 <br />\n在我的遠方 <br />\n明天，嗯，明天我要離開 <br />\n今天，嗯，今天且讓我 <br />\n再想念你 <br />\n最後一次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23a5f13cb957a94df54ef452558917bdeebe164","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:21:02.000Z","msg":"前人痛徹心扉，悲愴灑墨的情境，似乎能一脈相承。 <br />\n他們隔簾聽雨，舉樽獨喝。 <br />\n他們徹夜不眠，枕着孤獨。 <br />\n他們把酒問青天，為了得到答案。 <br />\n為了得到那人生中月缺月圓的真相。 <br />\n<br />\n我亦如是。"},{"pid":"7d44e4456e375fccdbbe81511e69cfdde6f42a0a","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"最後的晨曦，夏彭年與李平站在著名的歎息橋上。<br />\n<br />\n他眼睛酸澀，精神恍惚，聲音重濁。 <br />\n<br />\n她強自振作，心懷重壓，暗然銷魂。 <br />\n<br />\n整個天空是灰紫色的，只在東方有一絲魚肚白，雨水墮在河中，圈圈漣漪，煙霧濛濛。 <br />\n<br />\n他說：「景色美得叫人歎息。」 <br />\n<br />\n她說：「不止是這樣的緣故吧。」 <br />\n<br />\n「啊。」 <br />\n<br />\n「你看，彭年，人生就像一道橋，我們自彼處來，往那頭去，一邊走，一邊不住歎息，因恨事太多。」 <br />\n<br />\n夏彭年憐惜的問：「這些年來，也總有叫你高興的事。」 <br />\n<br />\n李平抬起頭，思想像是飛出老遠，過半晌她說：「現在我知道了，在那個時候，我也不是不快樂的。」 <br />\n<br />\n「現在呢？」 <br />\n<br />\n李平忽然笑了，過半晌她答：「現在，現在我也不是不快樂。」 <br />\n<br />\n她輕輕歎息一聲，轉過臉去。 <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來我非不快樂 <br />\n只我一人未發覺"},{"pid":"c87d1e7f4a8341f57cceaedfc547a41da5305cd3","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1a964fc5c8d63319b4cdada7dd949991d265ddd","tid":566144,"uid":97526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd7fbfbfe756c9046bbe6fa85469beb18a011c39","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:23:26.000Z","msg":"沒有公平 只有運氣 <br />\n有人找到他的莫敏兒 <br />\n有人窮一生之力也找不上 <br />\n世界總是如此 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T11:34:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求而不得 算不上找到 對不對?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:22:11.000Z","msg":"將來既自己會係點 <br />\n一沉不起 一蹶不振 <br />\n抑或重新出發 跌跌碰碰 繼續去找個值得你愛既人 <br />\n係你自己既選擇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dc865b79f73354c1cbbe84e17f0cd97e00eb2a","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:22:33.000Z","msg":"對於美孚新村的認識並不多， <br />\n只知它是第一個以中產階級為對象的大型屋苑。 <br />\n可以想像的是， <br />\n當年首批入住， <br />\n那些儒雅的中產人士， <br />\n如今都已退休了。 <br />\n早上上班的時候， <br />\n總會看到不少頭髮梳理齊整， <br />\n穿三件頭西裝的公公與打扮簡單優雅的婆婆， <br />\n手挽手的在散步。 <br />\n雖然美孚新村已經變得殘舊， <br />\n雖然露台前的海景已經不復見， <br />\n但公公婆婆坐在露台談天時， <br />\n依然可在眼前人的眼眸內看到無數風景。 <br />\n世界不過一點點的大。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  愛即永恆"},{"pid":"2b25705d6fae017732ceebea6d905b6f48750a7e","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T16:22:58.000Z","msg":"我知道這世界不是絕對的好 <br />\n我也知道它有離別　有衰老 <br />\n然而我只有一次的機會 <br />\n上主啊　請俯聽我的祈禱 <br />\n<br />\n請給我一個長長的夏季 <br />\n給我一段無瑕的回憶 <br />\n給我一顆溫柔的心 <br />\n給我一份結白的戀情 <br />\n<br />\n我只能來這世上一次　所以 <br />\n請再給我一個美麗的名字 <br />\n好讓他能在夜裏低喚我 <br />\n在奔馳的歲月裏 <br />\n永遠記得我們曾經相愛的事"},{"pid":"6f00255882af512a15128cb48b5bf9fc3992242c","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T11:02:58.000Z","msg":"如何承受這好奇 <br />\n你有沒有愛我的準備 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78755f2e340893650ea4ef5b07072c1cd36dd5db","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T11:03:20.000Z","msg":"「講多Ｄ野比你聽丫。從前有個女仔， <br />\n有一日病左，有個男仔係女仔屋企樓下買左一碗粥比佢食， <br />\n個女仔覺得呢碗粥係全世界最好食既粥。 <br />\n第二日，佢搵番個膠袋黎睇， <br />\n唔信就係係屋企樓下成日幫襯果間舖頭買既。於是，佢落去樓下再食一次。」 <br />\n<br />\n「個女仔落到粥舖，發覺今日既粥好難食，佢同自己講，冇理由既， <br />\n尋日果碗一定係第二度買既，亦都有可能係個男仔親手煮既， <br />\n佢甚至好憎係舖頭入麵食緊粥既人。 <br />\n而由果日開始，佢就堅持每日都要食粥，同時，亦都好迷失， <br />\n究竟所有粥，艇仔、豬紅、牛肉粥，其實都係一樣味道丫？ <br />\n定還是係每碗艇仔粥既味道都唔係一樣呢？」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a332bf813c562b3db246fbd00e6f0f579778a68f","tid":566144,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"The way of life can be free and beautiful. But we have lost the way<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}